<Slide>
    <h1>The Pipeline</h1>
    <ul>
        <Appear><li>Data Science introduces coding and analysis side-by-side</li></Appear>
        <Appear><li>Detracts from focus on content.</li></Appear>
        <Appear><li>Centralize the user experience to place the focus on statistics rather than the computation</li></Appear>
    </ul>
</Slide>

<Slide>
    <h1>In short...</h1>
    ISLE is a data analysis pipeline that unifies the experience for students to focus on content rather than computing.
